60.7	Charlotte's_Web	Charlotte's Web	Charlotte's Web is a children's novel by American author E. B. White, about a pig named Wilbur who is saved from being slaughtered by an intelligent spider named Charlotte. The book was first published in 1952, with illustrations by Garth Williams.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/fe/CharlotteWeb.png/200px-CharlotteWeb.png
